            text: '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t在表示同意或部分同意时，我们也可以使用 **True** 和 **Yes, but** 这种有用的词汇和短语。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="1" rowspan="2">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/63/79/v/176379/MOB_5.2.1.2.1_4.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>A:&nbsp;London&#39;s not as hot as Paris in the summer.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t伦敦夏天没有巴黎热。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>B: <strong>True</strong>.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t没错。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="1" rowspan="2">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/63/80/v/176380/MOB_5.2.1.2.1_5.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>A: London&#39;s not as hot as Paris in the summer.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t伦敦夏天没有巴黎热。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>B: <strong>Yes, but</strong> Paris isn&#39;t as expensive.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t是的，可巴黎没有伦敦费钱。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t像 **Well** 和 **Hmm** 等词可以给我们时间思考接下来要说的话。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="1" rowspan="2">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/63/81/v/176381/MOB_5.2.1.2.1_6.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>A: Which place is better?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t哪个地方更好？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>B: <strong>Well</strong>, Moscow is very nice.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t嗯，莫斯科非常漂亮。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan="2" style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/63/82/v/176382/MOB_5.2.1.2.1_7.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>A: Which location is cheaper?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t哪个地方更便宜？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 35%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>B: <strong>Hmm</strong>. I&#39;m not sure.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t嗯，我不确定。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
