            text: '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 80%">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<strong>宣布决定</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t使用 **decide**、**choose** 和 **agree**  等动词宣布已经做出的重要决定。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>We&#39;ve decided to</strong> book three rooms.</em></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们决定预订三个房间。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>We&#39;ve chosen to</strong> have presentations on the first day.</em></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们决定第一天做演示。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>We agreed to</strong> have the conference on the 5th.</em></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们决定把会议安排在五号。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t如您看到的，所有这些动词都可接 **to**  后再接动词。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
