            text: '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%;">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>故事事件的排序</strong><br />\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t使用类似表达开始故事。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/67/v/155367/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r1.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>At first,</strong> I didn&#39;t like him.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t起初，我不喜欢他。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/68/v/155368/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>In the beginning,</strong> he seemed unfriendly.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t刚开始，他看起来不是很友好。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t使用类似表达继续讲述故事。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/69/v/155369/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Later, </strong>we started talking in the break room.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t后来，我们在休息室开始交谈。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/70/v/155370/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r4.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>After that,</strong> we had lunch a couple of times.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t之后，我们一起吃过几次午饭。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/71/v/155371/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r5.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Next, </strong>we went on a date.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t接下来，我们约会了。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%;">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t使用类似表达结束故事。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/72/v/155372/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r6.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Finally, </strong>he asked me to marry him.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t最后，他要我嫁给他。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/53/73/v/155373/GE_%205.3.1.3.1_r7.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>In the end, </strong>we got married and had three children.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t最后，我们结婚，生了三个孩子。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
