            text: '<div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<strong>状态动词</strong><br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="700">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t有些动词不描述动作；它们描述状态、状况或形势。它们称为 **stative verbs**。注意，这些动词几乎从不用于 **-ing** 形式。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t类似 **see**、**hear** 和 **know** 的静态动词可描述你感知或理解的东西。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/54/00/v/155400/GE_%205.3.3.2.2_r1.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 38%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>hear </strong>birds outside.</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我听到外面有鸟叫。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t**have** 和 **own** 等静态动词可描述你拥有的东西。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/54/01/v/155401/GE_%205.3.3.2.2_r2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>She <strong>has </strong>a new car.</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t她有一辆新车。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t**love** 和 **hate** 等静态动词可描述你对某事的感受。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/54/02/v/155402/GE_%205.3.3.2.2_r3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>hate </strong>vegetables!</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我讨厌蔬菜！</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t记住：静态动词几乎从不用于 **-ing** 形式。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t**正确：**<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>know </strong>John.</em><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t**错误：**<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>am knowing</strong> John.</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
