            text: "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t**director** 是掌控影片制作的人。你可以使用动词 **direct**，描述导演所做的事情。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/55/24/v/155524/GE_%205.5.2.1.2_r5.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 45%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em>Jenny Lindstrom <strong>directed</strong> 15 movies during her long career. She was an incredible <strong>director</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 2%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\tJenny Linstrom 在她漫长的职业过程中拍摄了 15 部电影。她是一位了不起的导演。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t使用以下词语描述影片的不同组成部分。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/55/25/v/155525/GE_%205.5.2.1.2_r6.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>The <strong>special effects</strong> in &#39;Invasion of the Body Snatchers&#39; are terrible.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\tInvasion of the Body Snatchers' 的特效很差劲。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/55/26/v/155526/GE_%205.5.2.1.2_r7.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I love the <strong>costumes</strong> in historical dramas.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我喜欢历史题材影片中的服装。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/55/27/v/155527/GE_%205.5.2.1.2_r8.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>The <strong>plot</strong> of that horror movie is ridiculous.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t恐怖片的情节荒谬可笑。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/55/28/v/155528/GE_%205.5.2.1.2_r9.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I love the <strong>soundtrack</strong> of &#39;Casablanca.&#39;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我非常喜欢 'Casablanca' 的原声音乐。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
